      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 2. Contact Us {%- endcomment -%}
  <div id="modal-contact" class="lumu-modal">
    <div class="lumu-modal__content">
      <button class="lumu-modal__close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <h2 class="lumu-modal__title">Contact Us</h2>
      <div class="lumu-modal__body">
        <p>We are always here to help you with your inquiries.</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@lumu.pk</p>
        <p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Saturday, 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 3. Careers {%- endcomment -%}
  <div id="modal-careers" class="lumu-modal">
    <div class="lumu-modal__content">
      <button class="lumu-modal__close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <h2 class="lumu-modal__title">Careers at Lumu</h2>
      <div class="lumu-modal__body">
        <p>Join the e-commerce revolution! We are always on the lookout for bright, passionate talent to join our growing team.</p>
        <p>Send your resume and portfolio to <strong>careers@lumu.pk</strong>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 4. Press {%- endcomment -%}
  <div id="modal-press" class="lumu-modal">
    <div class="lumu-modal__content">
      <button class="lumu-modal__close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <h2 class="lumu-modal__title">Press & Media</h2>
      <div class="lumu-modal__body">
        <p>For all press releases, media inquiries, and public relations, please reach out directly to our dedicated media team.</p>
        <p><strong>Contact:</strong> media@lumu.pk</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 5. Lumu Ability {%- endcomment -%}
  <div id="modal-ability" class="lumu-modal">
    <div class="lumu-modal__content">
      <button class="lumu-modal__close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <h2 class="lumu-modal__title">Lumu's Ability Program</h2>
      <div class="lumu-modal__body">
        <p>At Lumu, we believe commerce should be inclusive. The Ability Program is dedicated to empowering differently-abled individuals by providing them seamless opportunities to sell and work within our ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 6. FAQ {%- endcomment -%}
  <div id="modal-faq" class="lumu-modal">
    <div class="lumu-modal__content">
      <button class="lumu-modal__close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <h2 class="lumu-modal__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="lumu-modal__body">
        <p><strong>Q: How long does shipping take?</strong><br>A: Standard air freight delivery takes 8-12 days across the GCC.</p>
        <p><strong>Q: Are my payments safe?</strong><br>A: Yes! Our checkout utilizes industry-leading encryption and verified payment gateways.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 7. Purchase Protection {%- endcomment -%}
  <div id="modal-protection" class="lumu-modal">
    <div class="lumu-modal__content">
      <button class="lumu-modal__close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <h2 class="lumu-modal__title">Purchase Protection</h2>
      <div class="lumu-modal__body">
        <p>Shop with 100% confidence. If your item does not arrive within the promised timeframe or differs from the description, our <strong>Purchase Protection</strong> guarantees a full review and return/refund.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 8. Partner With Lumu {%- endcomment -%}
  <div id="modal-partner" class="lumu-modal">
    <div class="lumu-modal__content">
      <button class="lumu-modal__close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <h2 class="lumu-modal__title">Partner With Lumu</h2>
      <div class="lumu-modal__body">
        <p>Are you a manufacturer, distributor, or logistics provider? Partner with the fastest-growing GCC marketplace today.</p>
        <p>Contact us at <strong>partners@lumu.pk</strong> to discuss integration.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 9. Seller FAQ {%- endcomment -%}
  <div id="modal-seller-faq" class="lumu-modal">
    <div class="lumu-modal__content">
      <button class="lumu-modal__close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <h2 class="lumu-modal__title">Seller FAQ</h2>
      <div class="lumu-modal__body">
        <p><strong>Q: What do I need to start selling?</strong><br>A: Valid business registration and a commitment to quality. Join our seller portal to register your inventory.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 10. Seller Terms {%- endcomment -%}
  <div id="modal-seller-terms" class="lumu-modal">
    <div class="lumu-modal__content">
      <button class="lumu-modal__close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <h2 class="lumu-modal__title">Seller Terms & Conditions</h2>
      <div class="lumu-modal__body">
        <p>By registering as a merchant on Lumu, you agree to adhere strictly to our quality control guidelines, timely dispatch policies, and customer dispute resolution frameworks. Ensuring end-buyer satisfaction is our top mutual priority.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    // Select all links that start with #modal-
    const modalLinks = document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#modal-"]');
    const closeButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.lumu-modal__close');
    const modals = document.querySelectorAll('.lumu-modal');

    // Open Modal
    modalLinks.forEach(link => {
      link.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        const targetId = this.getAttribute('href').substring(1);
        const targetModal = document.getElementById(targetId);
        if(targetModal) {
          targetModal.classList.add('is-open');
          document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden'; // Prevent background scrolling
        }
      });
    });

    // Close Modal via button
    closeButtons.forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
        this.closest('.lumu-modal').classList.remove('is-open');
        document.body.style.overflow = 'auto';
      });
    });

    // Close Modal by clicking outside content
    window.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
      if(e.target.classList.contains('lumu-modal')) {
        e.target.classList.remove('is-open');
        document.body.style.overflow = 'auto';
      }
    });
  });
</script>

